# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/x11-misc/xscreensaver/ChangeLog,v 1.397 2015/07/04 05:10:07 jer Exp $

*xscreensaver-5.33 (04 Jul 2015)

  04 Jul 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +xscreensaver-5.33.ebuild,
  +files/xscreensaver-5.33-gentoo.patch:
  Version bump.

  05 Mar 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild,
  -files/xscreensaver-5.29-pragma.patch:
  Old.

  03 Mar 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  add arm64 support, tested on A53 board

  28 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #533752

  27 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #533752

  24 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #533752

  23 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #533752

  21 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #533752

  01 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #533752

  31 Jan 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Depend on virtual/glu by stephen.smith3141 (bug #538362).

  31 Jan 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #533752

  01 Jan 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #533752

  29 Dec 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #533752).

  30 Nov 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  Old.

  29 Nov 2014; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #525680

*xscreensaver-5.32 (20 Nov 2014)

  20 Nov 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -xscreensaver-5.31.ebuild,
  +xscreensaver-5.32.ebuild, -files/xscreensaver-5.31-uint32_t.patch:
  Version bump.

*xscreensaver-5.31 (17 Nov 2014)

  17 Nov 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +xscreensaver-5.31.ebuild,
  +files/xscreensaver-5.31-pragma.patch,
  +files/xscreensaver-5.31-uint32_t.patch:
  Version bump.

  11 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #525680

  04 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #525680

  03 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #525680

  02 Nov 2014; Sven Vermeulen <swift@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild,
  xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Remove sec-policy/selinux-* dependency from DEPEND but keep in RDEPEND (bug
  #527698)

  02 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #525680

  01 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #525680

  31 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #525680

  30 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #525680

  19 Oct 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #525680).

  11 Sep 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Tarball got updated.

*xscreensaver-5.30 (11 Sep 2014)

  11 Sep 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +xscreensaver-5.30.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  22 Aug 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -xscreensaver-5.26.ebuild:
  Old.

  22 Aug 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #517054

  22 Aug 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild,
  +files/xscreensaver-5.29-pragma.patch:
  Fix building with sys-devel/gcc-4.5.4 (bug #519856 by Ulrich Fieseler). Add
  epatch_user.

  20 Aug 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  Really remove append-libs -lpthread.

  20 Aug 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  Remove append-libs -lpthread.

  13 Aug 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #517054

  11 Aug 2014; Chema Alonso <nimiux@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64 wrt bug #517054

  02 Aug 2014; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sparc stable wrt #517054

  27 Jul 2014; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #517054

  26 Jul 2014; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org>
  xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #517054

  19 Jul 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-5.29.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #517054).

