*xscreensaver-5.10 (10 Sep 2009)

  10 Sep 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +xscreensaver-5.10.ebuild, +files/xscreensaver-5.10-gentoo.patch,
  +files/xscreensaver-5.10-xfce.patch:
  Version bump.

  25 Aug 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
