  30 Apr 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  xscreensaver-5.08-r1.ebuild:
  Run plain eautoconf wrt #268016, thanks to Peter Alfredsen and Christer
  Ekholm for testing. Seems this needs to be autoconfed but not autoreconfed
  to work.

  30 Apr 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +files/xscreensaver-5.08-po-recreate.patch, xscreensaver-5.08-r1.ebuild:
  Apply a patch from Fedora CVS to fix translations. Don't run eautoreconf
  wrt #240958, instead only unset LINGUAS because zh matches zh_CN or zh_TW
  which causes CATALOG error wrt #113681.

